            We believe in teaching our youth to use their voices as a form of cultural affirmation, to raise awareness on issues that affect our communities, and to promote social activism.
            OLE works to build youth leadership capacity in several areas:
            <ul>
            <li>Inspire pro-social friendships, strong life and interpersonal skills, and instill a sense of hope in the future to opportunity youth.</li>
            <li>Improve youthâ€™s life outcomes by providing life skills and character development that will make them self-sufficient and help them make positive life choices.</li>
